								<div class="content">
									<h2 class="title is-size-4">Permanent</h1>
									<p class="subtitle is-size-5">
									Uses decentralized data storage technology to prevent information loss.
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</article>
					</div>
					<div class="column is-one-third">
						<article class="section has-background-white">
