							</figure>
							<div class="has-text-centered">
								<div class="content">
									<h1 class="title is-size-4">Open</h1>
									<p class="subtitle is-size-5">
										Everyone can upload data onto our platform. Data can be set for public view.
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</article>
					</div>
					<div class="column is-one-third">
